<plot>A hot summer in the middle of the 50's. A pioneer's camp. 12 years old Dimana and Todor, while being on a guard of honour at a giant monument of Stalin, experience their first kiss. Literally, Stalin's shadow shelters them but figuratively, it separates them...10 years later they meet in the same place. Todor is a Komsomol functionary, sent to crush a students' riot at a summer working brigade. This time their love has no inhibitions. But following his assignment, Todor succeeds in cheating the rebels and detaining them forcibly in the camp. The only one who refuses to obey is Dimana.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?318070</url></doc>
